oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Today's veterinarians are interested in learning how to improve their dispensing and merchandising techniques. Veterinarians are becoming concerned with this important, but often neglected "Art of Veterinary Medicine." They are not just interested in the traditional "Science of Veterinary Medicine."
